53 struct V_RHREXPORT matricesMsg: public rfbMsg {
54  matricesMsg()

57  , eye(rfbEyeMiddle)
58  , viewNum(-1)
59  , width(0)

63  {

81  bool operator==(const matricesMsg &other) const {
82 
83  if (eye != other.eye)
84  return false;
85  if (viewNum != other.viewNum)
86  return false;
87  if (width != other.width)
88  return false;
89  if (height != other.height)
90  return false;
91 
92  for (int i=0; i<16; ++i) {
93  if (model[i] != other.model[i])
94  return false;
95  if (view[i] != other.view[i])
96  return false;
97  if (proj[i] != other.proj[i])
98  return false;
99  if (head[i] != other.head[i])
100  return false;
101  }
102 
103  return true;
104  }
105 };

124  struct Light {
125  // as in OpenGL
126  uint8_t enabled;
127 
128  uint8_t pad[7];
129 
130  double position[4];
131

135

139 
140  double attenuation[3];
141 
142  Light()
143  {
144  memset(this, '\0', sizeof(*this));
145 
146  position[2] = 1;
147 
148  ambient[3] = 1;
149 
150  spot_direction[2] = -1;
151  spot_cutoff = 180;
152 
153  attenuation[0] = 1;
154  }
155 
156  bool operator!=(const Light &o) const {
157 
158  if (enabled != o.enabled)
159  return true;
160 
161  for (int i=0; i<4; ++i) {
162  if (position[i] != o.position[i])
163  return true;
164  if (ambient[i] != o.ambient[i])
165  return true;
166  if (diffuse[i] != o.diffuse[i])
167  return true;
168  if (specular[i] != o.specular[i])
169  return true;
170  }
171 
172  for (int i=0; i<3; ++i) {
173  if (spot_direction[i] != o.spot_direction[i])
174  return true;
175  if (attenuation[i] != o.attenuation[i])
176  return true;
177  }
178 
179  if (spot_cutoff != o.spot_cutoff)
180  return true;
181  if (spot_exponent != o.spot_exponent)
182  return true;
183 
184  return false;
185  }
186  };
187 
188  int16_t viewNum;
189  uint8_t pad[5];
190 
192  Light lights[NumLights];
193 
194  bool operator!=(const lightsMsg &o) const {
195  if (viewNum != o.viewNum)
196  return true;
197  for (int i=0; i<NumLights; ++i) {
198  if (lights[i] != o.lights[i])
199  return true;
200  }
201  return false;
202  }
203 };
